title: Photo: Bani J Just Had A Reunion With Her Bigg Boss Besties!
text:
Divya Rao Mar . 10 . 2017 
Ex Bigg Boss finalist Bani J was undoubtedly one of the most popular contestants in the house. Despite being nominated nearly every week, her fans managed to save her week after week. In the house, she shared a great bond with Gaurav Chopra . PS – There’s even a hashtag for the two – #GauBani ! She also spent a good amount of time with Rahul Dev and Karan Mehra . While we’ve seen her chilling with Gaurav post the show, she hung out with Karan too last night. Take a look. Gaurav Chopra, Bani J, Karan Mehra 
So many feels right there! 14
